ich I could cast if I have the mana. But with only {G} available, I can't cast it (costs 1G). So no, unless I have another source. But the Elves can't tap, so no. So the only play is Giant Growth.\r\n\r\nTherefore, the correct move is to cast Giant Growth targeting Llanowar Elves in response to Lightning Bolt. This would save the Elves, allowing me to keep my mana dork for future turns. That seems like the best line here.",
